-- Taiwan Airlines Cut Direct Flight Prices to Shanghai, Economic Daily Says
-- Weiyi Lim
-- 2010-06-17T22:45:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/taiwan-airlines-cut-direct-flight-prices-to-shanghai-economic-daily-says.html

          
          
             EVA Airways Corp. will cut the price
of its direct flights to Shanghai by as much as 30 percent from
July 1, the Economic Daily News reported, citing a company 
announcement. China Airlines Ltd. will also reduce the price of
its direct flights by as much as 10 percent, according to the 
Taipei-based Chinese-language daily.  
